HEADWORD: Multure
<hw>Mul"ture</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>multure</ets>, <ets>moulture</ets>, F. <ets>mouture</ets>, fr. L.
<ets>molitura</ets> a grinding, <ets>molere</ets> to grind. See
